When you open the working area you see a dashboard listing the work centers connected to his work area.

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000459-0/2PowerMES_ENU.jpg"><br>

In the example, the operator's device is located in the Robot work area for which 2 work centers / resources (machines) are operational.

In the control panel it is also visible that one machine is active, the other is stopped.

